                                <span>Por Carlos Mazza</span>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <article class="chapter-item disabled my-5 pb-4">
                            <figure class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                                <img src="/especial_1000_dias/imgs/capitulos/capa_economia.jpg" alt="Capa capítulo Economia">
                            </figure>
                            <div class="info-chapter d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                <span class="font-weight-bold">01/10</span>
                                <a href="" class="my-2 text-light font-weight-bold text-center">Ep.2 Economia</a>
                                <span>Por Armando Lima</span>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <article class="chapter-item disabled my-5 pb-4">
                            <figure class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                                <img src="/especial_1000_dias/imgs/capitulos/capa_pandemia.jpg" alt="Capa capítulo Pandemia">
                            </figure>
                            <div class="info-chapter d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
